Ask HN: Curated list of top AI models per function?
text:
I'm looking for a daily updated, opinionated catalog of best AI models, segregated per function. Both SaaS and open models. I mean functions like speech-to-text (Whisper etc), conversational (GPT-4 and open alternatives), text-to-speech, image generation, etc.

I prefer it to only list a tiny number of top-performing models per category. I do not want a bag of hundreds of models to research through.

Essentially, I want opinionated state-of-the-art tracker, because I can't keep up.
